        "start": 28,
        "end": 29
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "通「否」。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-32",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 2,
        "start": 80,
        "end": 81
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "理虧。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-33",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 2,
        "start": 98,
        "end": 102
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "比較這兩個對策。均︰衡量。之：此、這。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-34",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 2,
        "start": 103,
        "end": 109
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "寧可答應將和氏璧給予秦國（假如秦王受璧而不予城），使秦負上理虧的責任。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-35",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 2,
        "start": 127,
        "end": 128
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "倘若、如果。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-36",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 2,
        "start": 152,
        "end": 156
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "把璧玉完完整整地帶回趙國。「完璧歸趙」後來成為成語，表示物歸原主的意思。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-37",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 3,
        "start": 3,
        "end": 5
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "秦宮名。章臺本是供登臨遊樂的離宮，昭王不在正殿而在章臺召見趙國使臣藺相如，有輕視之意。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-38",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 3,
        "start": 56,
        "end": 57
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "玉石上的斑點。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-39",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 3,
        "start": 73,
        "end": 75
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "後退站立。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-40",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 3,
        "start": 79,
        "end": 84
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "憤怒得頭髮豎起頂着帽子，形容極度憤怒的樣子。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-41",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 3,
        "start": 120,
        "end": 121
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "倚仗、恃着。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-42",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 3,
        "start": 148,
        "end": 150
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "麻布衣服，借指平民百姓。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-43",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 3,
        "start": 172,
        "end": 173
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "同「歡」。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-44",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 3,
        "start": 182,
        "end": 184
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "古時候舉行祭祀，主祭的人先要齋戒，住在清淨的房子裏，不同外人往來，誠心誠意準備敬神。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-45",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 3,
        "start": 192,
        "end": 197
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "（相如）在朝廷上行了禮，送出國書。庭：通「廷」，國君聽政的朝堂。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-46",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 3,
        "start": 201,
        "end": 210
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "尊重大國的威嚴而表達敬意。嚴：尊重。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-47",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 3,
        "start": 217,
        "end": 221
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "於一般宮殿中（而不是正殿）接見微臣。觀：用作遊樂的宮殿，即指章臺。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-48",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 3,
        "start": 217,
        "end": 221
      },
      "kind": "pronunciation",
      "lang": "yue",
      "text": "貫；gun3",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-49",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 3,
        "start": 217,
        "end": 221
      },
      "kind": "pronunciation",
      "lang": "cmn",
      "text": "guàn",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-50",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 3,
        "start": 225,
        "end": 226
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "傲慢。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-51",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 3,
        "start": 225,
        "end": 226
      },
      "kind": "pronunciation",
      "lang": "yue",
      "text": "據；geoi3",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-52",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 3,
        "start": 225,
        "end": 226
      },
      "kind": "pronunciation",
      "lang": "cmn",
      "text": "jù",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-53",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 3,
        "start": 262,
        "end": 263
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "逼迫。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-54",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 4,
        "start": 5,
        "end": 6
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "斜視。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-55",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 4,
        "start": 5,
        "end": 6
      },
      "kind": "pronunciation",
      "lang": "yue",
      "text": "藝；ngai6",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-56",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 4,
        "start": 5,
        "end": 6
      },
      "kind": "pronunciation",
      "lang": "cmn",
      "text": "nì",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-57",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 4,
        "start": 21,
        "end": 25
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "於是婉言道歉，堅決請求藺相如不要這樣做。辭謝：婉言道歉。固請：堅決請求。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-58",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 4,
        "start": 26,
        "end": 42
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "召喚負責掌管版圖的官吏查考地圖，指着從這裏到那裏的十五座城給予趙國。有司：官吏的通稱。案：通「按」，查考、按照。都：城。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-59",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 4,
        "start": 45,
        "end": 46
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "揣度。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-60",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 4,
        "start": 45,
        "end": 46
      },
      "kind": "pronunciation",
      "lang": "yue",
      "text": "踱；dok6",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-61",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 4,
        "start": 45,
        "end": 46
      },
      "kind": "pronunciation",
      "lang": "cmn",
      "text": "duó",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-62",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 4,
        "start": 48,
        "end": 49
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "僅、只是。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-63",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 4,
        "start": 51,
        "end": 52
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "假裝。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-64",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 4,
        "start": 51,
        "end": 52
      },
      "kind": "pronunciation",
      "lang": "yue",
      "text": "羊；joeng4",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-65",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 4,
        "start": 51,
        "end": 52
      },
      "kind": "pronunciation",
      "lang": "cmn",
      "text": "yáng",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-66",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 4,
        "start": 111,
        "end": 116
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "在宮廷正殿上設九賓之禮。九賓：也稱「九儀」，古時外交上最隆重的禮節，由九個儐相依次傳呼接引上殿。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-67",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 5,
        "start": 17,
        "end": 18
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "安置，作動詞用。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-68",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 5,
        "start": 20,
        "end": 23
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "賓館名。傳：設於驛站的房舍。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-69",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 5,
        "start": 20,
        "end": 23
      },
      "kind": "pronunciation",
      "lang": "yue",
      "text": "攢；zyun3",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-70",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 5,
        "start": 20,
        "end": 23
      },
      "kind": "pronunciation",
      "lang": "cmn",
      "text": "zhuàn",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-71",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 5,
        "start": 44,
        "end": 46
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "穿着粗布便衣（裝扮成平民模樣）。衣：穿着，作動詞用。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-72",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 5,
        "start": 44,
        "end": 46
      },
      "kind": "pronunciation",
      "lang": "yue",
      "text": "意；ji3",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-73",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 5,
        "start": 44,
        "end": 46
      },
      "kind": "pronunciation",
      "lang": "cmn",
      "text": "yì",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-74",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 5,
        "start": 52,
        "end": 54
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "小路、便道。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-75",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 5,
        "start": 54,
        "end": 55
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "逃離、出走。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-76",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 6,
        "start": 35,
        "end": 37
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "即秦穆公，春秋五霸之一。繆：通「穆」。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-77",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 6,
        "start": 44,
        "end": 53
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "未曾有堅守信約的君主。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-78",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 6,
        "start": 72,
        "end": 76
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "已從偏僻的小路回到趙國了。間：「間道」的簡縮；或解作偷偷地。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-79",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 6,
        "start": 72,
        "end": 76
      },
      "kind": "pronunciation",
      "lang": "yue",
      "text": "諫；gaan3",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-80",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 6,
        "start": 72,
        "end": 76
      },
      "kind": "pronunciation",
      "lang": "cmn",
      "text": "jiàn",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-81",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 6,
        "start": 87,
        "end": 89
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "一個，有低小和微賤的意思。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-82",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 6,
        "start": 140,
        "end": 142
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "用滾湯烹煮罪犯，是古代酷刑。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-83",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 6,
        "start": 143,
        "end": 144
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "表示「希望」的語氣助詞。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-84",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 6,
        "start": 149,
        "end": 150
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "通「熟」，詳細。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-85",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 7,
        "start": 8,
        "end": 9
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "表示又驚又怒的聲音。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-86",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 7,
        "start": 56,
        "end": 67
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "趙王怎會因為一塊璧玉的緣故而欺騙我們秦國呢？邪：通「耶」。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-87",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 7,
        "start": 69,
        "end": 74
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "終於在朝廷上召見相如。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-88",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 7,
        "start": 94,
        "end": 100
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "出使諸侯之國，能不受欺辱。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-89",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 7,
        "start": 105,
        "end": 108
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "比卿低一級的官職。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-90",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 8,
        "start": 0,
        "end": 9
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "攻取了石城。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-91",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 8,
        "start": 31,
        "end": 43
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "想與趙王會面於西河外的澠池，以示友好。澠池：在今河南省澠池縣境。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-92",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 8,
        "start": 31,
        "end": 43
      },
      "kind": "pronunciation",
      "lang": "yue",
      "text": "敏；man5",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-93",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 8,
        "start": 31,
        "end": 43
      },
      "kind": "pronunciation",
      "lang": "cmn",
      "text": "miǎn",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-94",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 8,
        "start": 92,
        "end": 93
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "告別。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-95",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 8,
        "start": 99,
        "end": 100
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "估計。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-96",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 8,
        "start": 100,
        "end": 102
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "路程、里程。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-97",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 8,
        "start": 102,
        "end": 104
      },
      "kind": "semantic",
      "text": "會面。",
      "source": "cham"
    },
    {
      "id": "5-98",
      "range": {
        "type": "range",
        "scope": "verse",
        "verseIndex": 9,
        "start": 16,
